Features.

-A lighter, balanced assembly gives you a natural and stable fit
ㅤ

-Reduces distracting background noise

ㅤ

-Easy-to-use volume dial and mute switch

-Extra-long cable lets you position controls right where you want them for quick access
ㅤ

-Adjust up to 90 degrees for a personalized fit that sits flush on your ears

DESAIN RINGAN
